title: History made: In an astonishing Bronze Age discovery a 3000-year-old community has been unearthed
subtitle: This is the first news in object
body: The dig has been carried out under a large rectangular white tent sort of tent you might use for a wedding reception but here it's perched on the edge of a working quarry.Trial excavations followed in 2004 and 2006 when Bronze Age spearheads and a sword were found.
